<a name="clouds"></a>
<H2>Clouds and Sea</H2>
<a href="http://www.edit.ne.jp/~katsu/">Katsuaki HIRAMITSU</a> showed some images and talked about some of his shaders to create cool looking clouds and oceans.  Check out his <a href="http://www.edit.ne.jp/~katsu/img_index.htm">WEB page</a> (go to the CLOUD and SEA sections) to see some of those images and a little bit of background on them.<p>
Here are the smaller version of those images.  At his web page you will find larger versions.<p>
